{"title":"细雨如酥","authors":["王玉哲　高立林"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"细雨如酥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王玉哲　画　高立林　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把红伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚小太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雨中飘来飘去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨丝是透明的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树叶子上的经脉鲜嫩鲜嫩的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云拂过的山峰似水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映出了草滩和树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行走在这雨的世界里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把心的窗棂敞开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敞开给自然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明的雨丝飘洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心和眼睛也洗染得透亮啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚红红的小太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雨中升起，流着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雨丝不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雨丝不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只歌从大自然中淌出来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界都是透明的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点污染"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}